<PARAGRAPH>
A short bus ride into the Tian Shan Mountains brings one to Medeo, a popular tourist destination, with several hotels and an Olympic-size skating rink.
</PARAGRAPH>

<PARAGRAPH>
On 21 December, 1991, the Charter that ended the Soviet Union creating the Commonwealth of Independent States was signed there.</PARAGRAPH>
